### ---- DEVICE REGISTRY (8081) ----

### Get device
GET http://localhost:8081/device/sensor-009

### Create device 1
POST http://localhost:8081/device
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deviceId": "sensor-009",
    "name": "Smoke Detector",
    "location": "Server Room",
    "type": "smoke"
}

### Create device 2
POST http://localhost:8081/device
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deviceId": "b8:27:eb:bf:9d:51",
    "name": "Living Room Sensor",
    "location": "Living Room",
    "type": "multi"
}

### Create device 3
POST http://localhost:8081/device
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deviceId": "00:0f:00:70:91:0a",
    "name": "Kitchen Sensor",
    "location": "Kitchen",
    "type": "multi"
}

### Create device 4
