### ---- INGEST (8085) ----

### Send measurement
POST http://localhost:8085/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deviceId": "sensor-009",
    "temperature": 25.3,
    "humidity": 60.0,
    "co": 0.015,
    "lpg": 0.007,
    "smoke": 0.02,
    "light": true,
    "motion": false
}

### Send measurement
POST http://localhost:8085/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deviceId": "sensor-009",
    "temperature": 22.0,
    "humidity": 55.0,
    "co": 0.004,
    "lpg": 0.005,
    "smoke": 0.01,
    "light": false,
    "motion": false
}

