### ---- MONITORING (8082) ----

### Get device state
GET http://localhost:8082/monitoring/sensor-009/state

### ---- ALERT (8083) ----

### Get alerts for device
GET http://localhost:8083/alert/sensor-009

### ---- COMPOSITE (8084) ----

### Get full telemetry
GET http://localhost:8084/telemetry/sensor-009